{"municipality":"波佐見町","pref":"長崎県","muni_code":"423238","count":4,"items":[{"pref":"長崎県","municipality":"波佐見町","name":"皿山大神宮石像神殿","category":"有形文化財","subcategory":"建造物","designation":"町指定","designated_date":null,"location":null,"description":"室町中期の長享元年(1487)創建。石造神殿は明治初期、名工筒井関平作。構造・彫刻ともに芸術性が高く、平成3年(1991)補修。","source_url":"https://www.town.hasami.lg.jp/kiji0031442/index.html","source_format":"html","fetched_at":"2026-07-12T08:53:58Z","jmh_id":"JMH-423238-0003"},{"pref":"長崎県","municipality":"波佐見町","name":"浮立","category":"民俗文化財","subcategory":"無形民俗文化財","designation":"町指定","designated_date":null,"location":null,"description":"日照りの際に笛・鉦・太鼓で雨乞いをし、氏神の祭礼に奉納する芸能。野々川・山中(湯無田)・鬼木・協和の4地区で継承。","source_url":"https://www.town.hasami.lg.jp/kiji0031442/index.html","source_format":"html","fetched_at":"2026-07-12T08:53:58Z","jmh_id":"JMH-423238-0002"},{"pref":"長崎県","municipality":"波佐見町","name":"三領石","category":"記念物(史跡・名勝・天然記念物)","subcategory":"史跡","designation":"町指定","designated_date":null,"location":"村木郷","description":"寛保2年(1742)建立、旧佐賀藩領・大村藩領・平戸藩領の三領境を示す石碑。","source_url":"https://www.town.hasami.lg.jp/kiji0031442/index.html","source_format":"html","fetched_at":"2026-07-12T08:53:58Z","jmh_id":"JMH-423238-0001"},{"pref":"長崎県","municipality":"波佐見町","name":"稗ノ尾眼鏡橋","category":"有形文化財","subcategory":"建造物","designation":"町指定","designated_date":null,"location":"稗ノ尾河川公園内(移築)","description":"明治41年(1908)に石橋として架け換えられた眼鏡橋。永尾・三股両郷を結ぶ。現在は稗ノ尾河川公園内に移築。","source_url":"https://www.town.hasami.lg.jp/kiji0031442/index.html","source_format":"html","fetched_at":"2026-07-12T08:53:58Z","jmh_id":"JMH-423238-0004"}]}